<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reparación y Mantenimiento | TechRM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0c0b0b;
            --bg-panel: #151111;
            --card-bg: #1c1717;
            --card-inner: #271f1f;
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #aaa0a0;
            --accent-red: #ff7b7b;
            --accent-amber: #ffc66d;
            --accent-blue: #8ec7ff;
            --nav-bg: rgba(12, 11, 11, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .repair-hero {
            min-height: 640px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.95fr) minmax(360px, 1.05fr);
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 9rem 6% 5rem;
            background:
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(12, 11, 11, 0.98), rgba(12, 11, 11, 0.76)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1800') center/cover;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .eyebrow {
            color: var(--accent-red);
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        }

        .repair-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.2rem);
            line-height: 0.98;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .repair-hero h1 span { color: var(--accent-red); }

        .repair-hero p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 620px;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-service {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.35rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-service:hover,
        .btn-service:focus {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 123, 123, 0.55);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        }

        .btn-primary-service {
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: #3a0707;
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        .lead-form {
            align-self: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 123, 123, 0.34);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(21, 17, 17, 0.9);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        }

        .lead-form h2 {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
        }

        .lead-form p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #ffd0d0;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        input,
        select,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 0.82rem 0.9rem;
        }

        textarea { resize: vertical; }

        .form-submit {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 46px;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: #3a0707;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .success-banner {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 0.9rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.42);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.12);
            color: #bdf4d0;
            font-size: 0.86rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .diagnostic-board {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(21, 17, 17, 0.82);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .board-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent-red);
            box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 123, 123, 0.6);
        }

        .board-row:nth-child(2) .status-dot { background: var(--accent-amber); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 198, 109, 0.45); }
        .board-row:nth-child(3) .status-dot { background: var(--accent-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(142, 199, 255, 0.45); }

        .board-row h2 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .board-row span,
        .board-row p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1180px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-heading {
            display: flex;
            align-items: end;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-heading h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        .section-heading p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 460px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .repair-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .repair-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.35rem;
        }

        .repair-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: #3a0707;
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .repair-tag.amber { background: var(--accent-amber); color: #3a2500; }
        .repair-tag.blue { background: var(--accent-blue); color: #08233d; }

        .repair-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        }

        .repair-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
        }

        .timeline {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            background: var(--bg-panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .timeline-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-step {
            background: var(--card-inner);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.1rem;
        }

        .timeline-step strong {
            display: inline-flex;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: #3a0707;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .timeline-step h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-step p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
        }

        .cta-panel {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 123, 123, 0.14), var(--bg-panel));
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .cta-panel h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .cta-panel p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 3rem 6%;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .light-mode {
            --bg-color: #fff8f8;
            --bg-panel: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: #fffafa;
            --card-inner: #ffffff;
            --card-border: rgba(76, 29, 29, 0.12);
            --text-main: #2b1a1a;
            --text-muted: #654f4f;
            --accent-red: #c24141;
            --accent-amber: #b45309;
            --accent-blue: #0b74d1;
            --nav-bg: rgba(255, 250, 250, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(76, 29, 29, 0.08);
        }

        .light-mode .repair-hero {
            background:
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 248, 248, 0.98), rgba(255, 248, 248, 0.84)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1800') center/cover;
        }

        .light-mode .diagnostic-board,
        .light-mode .board-row {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        }

        .light-mode .lead-form {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            border-color: rgba(194, 65, 65, 0.22);
        }

        .light-mode .form-group label {
            color: #713333;
        }

        .light-mode input,
        .light-mode select,
        .light-mode textarea {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-color: rgba(76, 29, 29, 0.14);
        }

        .light-mode .success-banner {
            background: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.24);
            color: #166534;
        }

        .light-mode .cta-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(194, 65, 65, 0.1), #ffffff);
        }

        .light-mode .nav-links a.active {
            color: #c24141;
            border-bottom-color: #c24141;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .repair-hero,
            .cta-panel {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .repair-grid,
            .timeline-grid,
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }

            .lead-form { align-self: auto; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .repair-hero {
                padding: 8rem 1.25rem 3rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .repair-grid,
            .timeline-grid,
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .section-heading { display: block; }
            .section-heading p { margin-top: 1rem; }
            .container { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
            footer { flex-direction: column; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <header class="repair-hero">
        <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Diagnóstico y reparación</div>
            <h1>Cuando algo falla, buscamos la causa <span>antes de cambiar piezas.</span></h1>
            <p>Reparamos equipos que no arrancan, se calientan, hacen ruido, van lentos o presentan fallos intermitentes. El objetivo es darte una explicación clara y una solución realista.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="#solicitud">Pedir diagnóstico</a>
                <a class="btn-service" href="/hardware">Volver a hardware</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <form class="lead-form" id="solicitud" action="/solicitar-reparacion" method="POST">
            <h2>Solicita diagnóstico rápido</h2>
            <p>Cuéntanos el síntoma principal y te orientamos con el siguiente paso.</p>
            <% if (success) { %>
                <div class="success-banner">Solicitud enviada. Te responderemos lo antes posible.</div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Tu nombre" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="contacto">Contacto</label>
                    <input type="text" id="contacto" name="contacto" placeholder="Email o teléfono" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="dispositivo">Equipo</label>
                    <input type="text" id="dispositivo" name="dispositivo" placeholder="PC, portátil, modelo...">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="urgencia">Urgencia</label>
                    <select id="urgencia" name="urgencia">
                        <option>Normal</option>
                        <option>Express</option>
                        <option>No estoy seguro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="descripcion">Qué le pasa</label>
                <textarea id="descripcion" name="descripcion" rows="3" placeholder="No enciende, se calienta, va lento, hace ruido..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <button class="form-submit" type="submit">Solicitar diagnóstico</button>
        </form>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="fallos">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Qué revisamos</h2>
                <p>La reparación se enfoca como diagnóstico: identificar síntomas, aislar la causa y aplicar la solución con menos ensayo y error.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="repair-grid">
                <article class="repair-card">
                    <span class="repair-tag">Averías</span>
                    <h3>No arranca o se apaga</h3>
                    <p>Revisión de fuente, placa, memoria, GPU, discos y cableado interno.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="repair-card">
                    <span class="repair-tag amber">Mantenimiento</span>
                    <h3>Ruido y temperatura</h3>
                    <p>Limpieza interna, ventiladores, pasta térmica y curva de refrigeración.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="repair-card">
                    <span class="repair-tag blue">Optimización</span>
                    <h3>Lentitud o bloqueos</h3>
                    <p>Diagnóstico de almacenamiento, sistema, procesos, RAM y salud general.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="timeline">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Proceso técnico</h2>
                <p>Un recorrido claro para que sepas en qué punto está tu equipo y qué se va a hacer.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-grid">
                <article class="timeline-step">
                    <strong>1</strong>
                    <h3>Recepción</h3>
                    <p>Registramos síntomas y estado físico del equipo.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-step">
                    <strong>2</strong>
                    <h3>Diagnóstico</h3>
                    <p>Aislamos la causa con pruebas de hardware y software.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-step">
                    <strong>3</strong>
                    <h3>Solución</h3>
                    <p>Aplicamos reparación, limpieza, ajuste o sustitución.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-step">
                    <strong>4</strong>
                    <h3>Validación</h3>
                    <p>Probamos estabilidad, temperatura y rendimiento final.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-panel">
            <div>
                <h2>¿No sabes si reparar o actualizar?</h2>
                <p>Si la reparación no compensa, te lo diremos. Puedes comparar con asesoría o pasar a montaje si conviene empezar desde cero.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="/asesoria-hardware">Comparar opciones</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="logo">TECHRM</div>
        <div>© 2026 TECHRM. Diagnóstico claro antes de tocar el equipo.</div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
